README (English)
--------------------------------
This directory contains tools to generate translation files for a new
languages or to update translation files for existing languages.

See PowerERP Wiki page:
https://wiki.powererp.org/index.php/Translator_documentation
For more information on how to use them.

Translation of PowerERP Project at Transifex:
https://www.transifex.com/powererp-association/powererp/dashboard/


Installation of Transifex Client:
---------------------------------
for Linux OS
to install or to update transifex client: 
sudo pip install --upgrade transifex-client


Comparison of Terms between ERPs
---------------------------------
https://wiki.powererp.org/index.php?title=Comparison_of_Terms_between_ERPs
